# Environment files — Vite bakes VITE_* vars into the build at compile time,
# so a committed .env.production with a dev (pk_test_) Clerk key ships the
# dev key in the production JS bundle. Block all .env* from being tracked
# except documented templates ending in .example.
# Caught 2026-05-17: prod was running pk_test_ in compiled JS because
# frontendts/.env.production was untracked and never reviewed. The file
# stays on disk for local builds — only git tracking is blocked.
.env
.env.*
!.env.*.example

# Editor directories and files
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

*.tsbuildinfo

# opensrc - source code for packages
opensrc/
